title: King tides are coming and you can help the state document them
description: The California Coastal Commission is collecting photos and videos from the public to assess how rising sea levels may affect coastal areas in the future.
content:
King tides the highest tides of the year will begin to flow toward San Diegos coast on Thursday morning, and the state is asking the public to help document them.
